
Bicycle
=======

[] basic schematic
[] breadboard of device


[] get MIDI in
[] record to buffer
[] end record on "end hit"
[] playback buffer
[] merge with buffer
[] clear on record
[] "the one" output trigger

[] process output midi
	[] output to MIDI on another set of channels
	[] output to output handler (see below)

[] channel to differentiate two channels of loop
[] note velocity to CV V
[] radius CC to CV R
[] note on / off to trig 1

[] mute control (keeps things playing)






